{"tid":2360650,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"中國係真小人既極致，美國係偽君子既極致","createTime":"2021-01-10T03:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T17:59:04.000Z","uid":140967,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16a1666174f35b0754ce958639ed9621fc6a7eb7","tid":2360650,"uid":140967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:45:08.000Z","msg":"自大選到宜家侵侵俾全美國各方杯葛，真係覺得美國大多數主流都好醜陋，噁心程度比中國高好多<br />\n<br />\n中國就共產黨擺明車馬做壞事<br />\n美國就俾成班左膠恐怖份子操控<br />\n<br />\n如果美國係由班咁既人組成既國家，將來真係被滅國都唔可惜，死撚晒佢啦垃圾左膠"},{"pid":"37515d9a1c30e877106241feeb114b20eeb61691","tid":2360650,"uid":261819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"【#美國國會衝擊】白思豪聯同多名國會議員公開要求特朗普下台，有眾議員再促請彭斯及內閣行動，否則國會復會將推動彈劾。<br />\n<br />\n▸相關報道：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3ovwfXZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ovwfXZ&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=1cc6b1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3ovwfXZ</a>"},{"pid":"49f27756e28507c5ea8483f36b1f31685de75f6c","tid":2360650,"uid":201930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"外太空返黎？ 政治唔係不嬲都咁架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900a3c5047f905fd4c2d240a4080a1cc86e69cd6","tid":2360650,"uid":357710,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"49f27756e28507c5ea8483f36b1f31685de75f6c","tid":2360650,"uid":201930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"外太空返黎？ 政治唔係不嬲都咁架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:43:33.000Z","msg":"國家越大越小氣&nbsp;,&nbsp;不過咁講這裡一定有人接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6412cfe1fe457921a7a309b30d3b2cf176cfd019","tid":2360650,"uid":146621,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"今次對美國真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰撚過共慘黨"},{"pid":"acb422ab38fbd0e8a39fc3c3588f32d18980c8c7","tid":2360650,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:16:38.000Z","msg":"假民主既美國<br />\n唔見得光既光明會<br />\n縮頭烏龜既影子政府"},{"pid":"91fdf7b980d1db80ca51351ced374335c7bdd38a","tid":2360650,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"乜撚野民主燈塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌佢老味聽完袁爸呢集<br />\n屌佢老味個燈膽燒生製造架<br />\n黑撚到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AHxxyWb6J6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAHxxyWb6J6s&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=4c5117df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AHxxyWb6J6s</a><br />\n我敢講，美國所謂既民主？<br />\n單單都講緊2年前，3年前，未競選年之前<br />\n美國既民主同支那有乜撚野分別？<br />\n我敢講呀，美國早喺斯洛登爆料果陣<br />\n美國政治已經黑撚到仆街<br />\n純粹因為一堆反支那行政睇落以為民主燈塔<br />\n事實上，支那臭蟲論抵佢咁大口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就一丘之貉<br />\n<br />\n有反共總理既國家，真係要好好珍惜<br />\n但數黎數去，居然得印度澳洲同北韓似樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好聽某條撚樣講打國際線打兩邊<br />\n你試下hocc求拜登救港丫？救咗未呀？<br />\n試下叫佢批評下契媽丫<br />\n<br />\n人既力量係好弱，但國際線上，<br />\n始終要世界比翻壓力去美國同埋聯合國<br />\n唯有由底層開始，令世人覺醒<br />\n與其遊說政務官<br />\n例不如由街客開始"},{"pid":"fb784becc8d23e769939102e0995b4b4bab8c01d","tid":2360650,"uid":310275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49f27756e28507c5ea8483f36b1f31685de75f6c","tid":2360650,"uid":201930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"外太空返黎？ 政治唔係不嬲都咁架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"政治本身就係咁，係比連登仔輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a44ed2cbd7d6028a6705ea4d01a4bf44428be7","tid":2360650,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb784becc8d23e769939102e0995b4b4bab8c01d","tid":2360650,"uid